### Product Service API Requests
# 服务基础地址（可在环境变量中配置）
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8082

### ==============================================
### 1. 健康检查接口
### ==============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### ==============================================
### 2. 商品查询接口（公开）
### ==============================================

### 分页查询商品列表（默认参数）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Accept: application/json

### 分页查询商品列表（自定义分页+分类）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=1&size=5&category=手机数码
Accept: application/json

### 根据SKU查询单个商品
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/SKU001
Accept: application/json

### 根据分类查询商品
< {%
    request.variables.set("category", encodeURIComponent("手机数码"));
%}

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/category/{{category}}
Accept: application/json

### ==============================================
### 3. 商品管理接口（需网关鉴权，测试用）
### ==============================================

### 创建商品
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {JWT_TOKEN}  # 实际环境由网关校验

{
  "sku": "SKU001",
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro",
  "description": "苹果最新旗舰手机",
  "price": "7999.00",
  "stock": 100,
  "category": "手机数码",
  "status": 1
}

### 全量更新商品
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/SKU001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {JWT_TOKEN}

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro Max",
  "description": "苹果超大杯旗舰",
  "price": "8999.00",
  "category": "手机数码",
  "status": 1
}

### 仅更新商品库存（订单服务专用接口）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/products/SKU001/stock
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {JWT_TOKEN}

# delta：库存变动量（正数增加，负数扣减）
{
  "delta": -10
}